token_info.name: Mystery Fish Token :: Series II
token_info.description: Burning this token will breed your own unique Mystery Fish. Each fish has their own tank to live in, complete with plants and up to 2 ornaments and 1-3 snail friends. Once minted, your fish, snail/s & ornament/s are fixed - but the plants will update everyday with new colours and arrangements to stay fresh.  Series II is limited to 1000 fishies. Each one unique to the breeder. Visit http://mystery.fish or @shig_nft for more information and upcoming Mystery Fish news
